{"tid":1425693,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"攻擊性武器","createTime":"2019-08-06T19:38:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T19:44:22.000Z","uid":280182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e819b4903d8bb5b58cd0214a119bf65958f99a86","tid":1425693,"uid":280182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:38:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2280530778873808&amp;id=100007507248829\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2280530778873808%26id%3D100007507248829&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=3e24e4c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2280530778873808&amp;id=100007507248829</a><br />\n阿sir講得啱，原本該物件冇攻擊性，但攞去襲擊人便算藏有攻擊性武器。<br />\n<br />\n話明攻擊性武器，給人感覺梗係會好血淋淋，諗起都好忟憎，一忟憎就好容易掟啲攻擊性武器，<br />\n所以阿sir都只是防犯於未燃。<br />\n<br />\n題外話，話說小妹我呢幾日都有啲心情煩躁，有冇姊妹同我一樣呢？<br />\n<br />\n#明嘅人就會明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1FwO2AG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1FwO2AG.png&h=90475c95&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7a8ca921040b09a788e491e5f24f02a220d3d677","tid":1425693,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:39:28.000Z","msg":"要好近先會中"},{"pid":"18487dc8f205b5b1b8efe7e31b7d8bd6439d270a","tid":1425693,"uid":212681,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T19:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de29307dcc4d4f9c7484b6513082f91cc31b15d","tid":1425693,"uid":280182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":